ion of Toner and Tu at very large length-scales. The derived framework\nis therefore general and it may describe the collective motion of any strongly\npolarized active matter system.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 5 Mar 2014 17:46:46 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 21 Jan 2015 10:16:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-02-05"}
